<p>Head turner: The songstress appeared in her element as she posed for photos in the Fendi outfit before she joined the likes of Yazmin Le Bon and Ashley Graham at the fashion showcase</p>

<p>The songstress appeared in her element as she posed for photos in the Fendi outfit before she joined the likes of Yazmin Le Bon and Ashley Graham at the fashion showcase.</p>

<p>The Italian house opened Milan Fashion Week at the Palazzo della Civiltà Italiana in Rome, which also houses the brand’s headquarters.</p>

<p>Ahead of the event WWD reported CEO Serge Brunschwig said the show will be 'a physical event, with a limited number of guests and a digital component, the format of which is being defined.'</p>

<p>Exciting: The Italian house opened Milan Fashion Week at the Palazzo della Civiltà Italiana in Rome, which also houses the brand’s headquarters</p>

<p>On trend: On the catwalk, red and white were the predominant colours. Models headed down the runway in a variety floaty sheer dresses, structured suits and tulle skirts</p>

<p>On the catwalk, red and white were the predominant colours. </p>

<p>Models headed down the runway in a variety floaty sheer dresses, structured suits and tulle skirts. </p>

<p>The brand's signature F motif was also printed on a number of pieces from the collection. </p>

<p>Socially-distanced: A small selection of guests watched the show</p>

<p>Rita has spent the summer holidaying in Ibiza and Greece with her new boyfriend Romain Gavras, 39.</p>

<p>The singer and the French director were first seen together in July after a night of partying.  </p>

<p>Speaking to The Sun, friends insisted Rita was involved with the filmmaker after she was seen enjoying a boozy evening out with business tycoon Faton Gashi.</p>

<p>A source said: 'Rita was hitting the town with friends including Faton. But she's in a serious thing with Romain and properly loved up. It's the first time she's been serious with someone in ages.'</p>

<p>Rita's previous boyfriends include Calvin Harris, Andrew Garfield, Rob Kardashian, musician Andrew Watt and Ricky Hil - the son of fashion designer Tommy Hilfiger. </p>

